    "description": "This fan game is a mix of visual novel and POINT &amp; CLICK genres. Created solely for the purpose of learning how to work with the Renpy engine and release games on the Steam platform. Distribution of the game is absolutely free.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThe game was created based on the lore of the character 'Anna Amur Tiger'.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nAll rights to the characters belong to their owners - links can be found in the main menu item &quot;About&quot;<br />\r\n<br />\r\nIn this game you have to deliver a package to Anna! Find out where the tiger is hiding! Deliver the package and don't stop until you succeed. Remember, nothing is what it seems...<br />\r\n<br />\r\nYou will find several endings, many secrets, references, dead ends... Explore the house inside and out, and find everything you can.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nAttention - English is presented in the form of machine translation.",
